				\begin{document}$$D=\frac{{\Vert E-W\ast C\Vert }_{FRO}}{\sqrt{p\ast n}}$$\end{document}D=‖E−W∗C‖FROp⁎n

D represents the p-by-n residual error matrix with p indicating the number of muscles, n the number of time bins and s the number of synergies.\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
